      "content": "that's a really good start for the tone. can you go a bit deeper into the rationale? like, have him explain to the crew why they specifically should feel a sense of duty toward the tribes. maybe mention some of the 'traits' or 'characteristics' he's observed in the people there that make them so incapable of governing themselves without outside help. make it sound like he's making a logical, even scientific, argument for their supervision.",
